{
  "stem": "15768.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "And after I got that-- over that initial fear, where a stallion chased my cow, knocked over the pail, and all my milk went into the dewy grass, I learned very quickly to pull out the pail and my stool [LAUGHS] and sort of blended into the fog.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "But somehow, I, I don't even think of it as a, as a dreadful ordeal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "Because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we accepted it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There, there were German soldiers in the area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew that there-- we heard that they were on the road.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have any really bad reports.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes people would come from a distance and say, this-- where there were large concentrations of Jewish refugees.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they would come with unpleasant stories.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we felt fairly, fairly safe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was our daily activity.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was still not very strong.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was not well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so her job was to be in the kitchen and help the farmer's wife put up vegetables and fruits in cans and jars and things of that nature.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she was more, more oriented towards household things, rather than the outdoor work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But everybody else was very busy in the fields.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of the things that my friend and I did a lot was we were supposed to gather eggs from the hen house.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we would stop.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we would sneak a raw egg and punch a hole in it and have our breakfast, a raw egg, which was like a miracle after not having had any really nourishing food for such a long period of time since we had left Brussels.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We really considered it a treat to be able to have food nearby.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the farmer's wife, of course, baked her own bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
